{"an6.106:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 6.106 ","an6.106:0.2":"10. Anisamsavagga ","an6.106:0.3":"Tanhasutta ","an6.106:1.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, tanha pahatabba, tayo ca mana. ","an6.106:1.2":"Katama tisso tanha pahatabba? ","an6.106:1.3":"Kamatanha, bhavatanha, vibhavatanha—","an6.106:1.4":"ima tisso tanha pahatabba. ","an6.106:1.5":"Katame tayo mana pahatabba? ","an6.106:1.6":"Mano, omano, atimano—","an6.106:1.7":"ime tayo mana pahatabba. ","an6.106:1.8":"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ima tisso tanha pahina honti, ime ca tayo mana; ","an6.106:1.9":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu acchecchi tanham, vivattayi samyojanam, samma manabhisamaya antamakasi dukkhassa”ti. ","an6.106:1.10":"Ekadasamam. ","an6.106:1.11":"Anisamsavaggo dasamo. ","an6.106:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","an6.106:2.1":"Patubhavo anisamso, ","an6.106:2.2":"aniccadukkhaanattato; ","an6.106:2.3":"Nibbanam anavatthi, ","an6.106:2.4":"ukkhittasi atammayo; ","an6.106:2.5":"Bhava tanhayeka dasati. ","an6.106:2.6":"Dutiyo pannasako samatto. "}